---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="AuditWeb privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 prose">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: March 28, 2026</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you use our website audit services or contact forms, we collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Contact information:</strong> name, email address</li>
      <li><strong>Website URL:</strong> the site you want audited</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> pages visited, time on site, referral source (via Google Analytics)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To deliver your website audit report</li>
      <li>To respond to your enquiries</li>
      <li>To improve our website and services</li>
      <li>To send relevant updates (only with your consent)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our site. Analytics cookies are only activated after you provide consent via our cookie banner. You can reject cookies at any time.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>StaticForms:</strong> processes form submissions</li>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> website analytics (with consent)</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> hosting and CDN</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your contact information for as long as necessary to provide our services. You can request deletion at any time by contacting us.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Under GDPR and similar regulations, you have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. Contact us at privacy@auditweb.site to exercise these rights.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy questions, email <a href="mailto:privacy@auditweb.site">privacy@auditweb.site</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
